== 製作 ==
電影的劇本本是列於黑名單中。喜歡劇本的[[克蘿伊·摩蕾茲|克蘿伊·摩蕾茲]]最初有望出演，但因行程有所衝突而放棄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/arnold-schwarzenegger-boarding-zombie-project-maggie-exclusive-1200500610/|title=Arnold Schwarzenegger Boarding Zombie Project ‘Maggie’ (EXCLUSIVE)|last=McNary|first=Dave|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2013-06-21|accessdate=2015-04-09|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205184005/https://variety.com/2013/film/news/arnold-schwarzenegger-boarding-zombie-project-maggie-exclusive-1200500610/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影於2013年9月23日在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的[[紐奧良|紐奧良]]開拍<ref>{{cite twitter|number=382194160628793345|user=Schwarzenegger|author=Schwarzenegger, Arnold|date=2013-09-23|accessdate=2015-04-09|title=Really excited to start shooting Maggie today with our director @henryhobson and my fantastic co-star, @yoabbaabba.}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2013/10/arnold_schwarzenegger_abigail.html|title=Arnold Schwarzenegger, Abigail Breslin joined by Joely Richardson in NOLA-shot 'Maggie'|last=Scott|first=Mike|work=[[The_Times-Picayune|The Times-Picayune]]|date=2013-10-03|accessdate=2015-04-09|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729214327/http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2013/10/arnold_schwarzenegger_abigail.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
《我的殭屍女兒》獲得褒貶不一的評價，影評人大為稱讚史瓦辛格與貝絲琳的演出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2015/04/23/review-maggie-deconstructs-zombie-films-schwarzenegger-and-breslin-shine/|title=Review - 'Maggie' Deconstructs Zombie Films, Schwarzenegger And Breslin Shine|last=Hughes|first=Mark|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2015-04-23|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227024517/https://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2015/04/23/review-maggie-deconstructs-zombie-films-schwarzenegger-and-breslin-shine/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/festivals/maggie-review-arnold-schwarzenegger-abigail-breslin-1201477855/|title=Tribeca Film Review: ‘Maggie’|last=Lodge|first=Guy|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety (magazine)]]|date=2015-04-23|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925132151/https://variety.com/2015/film/festivals/maggie-review-arnold-schwarzenegger-abigail-breslin-1201477855/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/tribeca-review-arnold-schwarzeneggers-zombie-movie-maggie-20150423|title=Tribeca Review: Arnold Schwarzenegger's Zombie Movie 'Maggie'|last=Jagernauth|first=Kevin|work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|date=2015-04-23|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425222846/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/tribeca-review-arnold-schwarzeneggers-zombie-movie-maggie-20150423|archive-date=2015-04-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://spinoff.comicbookresources.com/2015/04/24/tribeca-review-schwarzeneggers-maggie-isnt-the-zombie-movie-you-expect/|title=Tribeca Review: Schwarzenegger’s ‘Maggie’ Isn’t the Zombie Movie You Expect|last=Puchko|first=Kristy|work=[[Comic_Book_Resources|Comic Book Resources]]|date=2015-04-24|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422041644/http://spinoff.comicbookresources.com/2015/04/24/tribeca-review-schwarzeneggers-maggie-isnt-the-zombie-movie-you-expect/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.themarysue.com/maggie-movie-review/|title=Review: Maggie Is an Imperfect But Enjoyable Zombie Drama|last=Van Winkle|first=Dan|work=themarysue.com|date=2015-04-24|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2019-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424002340/https://www.themarysue.com/maggie-movie-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/arnold-schwwarzenegger-maggie-review-tri/|title=Arnold Schwarzenegger’s Dramatic Chops Go to Waste in ‘Maggie’ [Tribeca Review]|last=Han|first=Angie|work=[[我的殭屍女兒/Film|我的殭屍女兒//Film]]|date=2015-04-24|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125221602/https://www.slashfilm.com/arnold-schwwarzenegger-maggie-review-tri/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但也批評故事性的不足。

[[Twitch_Film|Twitch Film]]網站的克里斯多福·包恩審查了2015年的[[翠貝卡電影節|翠貝卡電影節]]，稱史瓦辛格：「在這裡他呈現了最好、最有成效的演出，比起以往的任何時刻都還最具調節和內斂。他擁有令人驚訝的細微差距和深度，他的角色是作為一名父親拼命戰鬥來維護他女兒的最後時刻，其遭受的痛苦極大，沒有能力扭轉或改善瑪姬的不可避免的衰落」，並補充說，「他的轉變證明了已經有本事去演更廣的角色，因為他已經知道了他已接近70歲，不太能承擔動作英雄角色的體能需求」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://twitchfilm.com/2015/04/tribeca-2015-review-maggie-an-elegant-zombie-melodrama.html|title=Tribeca 2015 Review: MAGGIE, An Elegant Zombie Melodrama|last=Bourne|first=Christopher|work=[[Twitch_Film|Twitch Film]]|date=2015-04-24|accessdate=2015-04-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427144526/http://twitchfilm.com/2015/04/tribeca-2015-review-maggie-an-elegant-zombie-melodrama.html|archivedate=2015-04-27}}</ref>。

[[Collider_(網站)|Collider]]網站的派瑞·涅米羅夫給了電影好壞參雜的評價，指出史瓦辛格：「永不會完全是超級硬朗的外表，但在這裡他肯定給人一個慈父的印象」，此外貝絲琳「獲得怪異的殭屍妝是一個很好的幫助，但她所賣的瑪姬最大的是一個試圖與被嚇壞的家人保持距離的強大少女，特別是令人揪心的演出」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://collider.com/maggie-review-arnold-schwarzenegger-abigail-breslin/|title=MAGGIE Review: Tribeca 2015|last=Nemiroff|first=Perri|work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|date=2015-04-24|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428013359/http://collider.com/maggie-review-arnold-schwarzenegger-abigail-breslin/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]網站基於84位專業影評人持有51％的新鮮度，平均得分5.6／10；該網站的評論家共識：「《我的殭屍女兒》有些時候有點拙劣，但部分由其強烈的演出和出乎意料的貼心而挽回整體基調」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/maggie_2015/ |title=Maggie |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2021-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319071035/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/maggie_2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根據28條影評，得分52（滿分100），好壞平均參雜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/maggie|title=Maggie|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=month 05, 2015|archive-date=2020-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401073312/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/maggie|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

